{"type":"message","id":"e50cfa10","parentId":"42d9495a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T06:46:43.328Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_etq9p7lrpq1l_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 4568\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='src/tic_classifier.py' new_len=3142\r\n[mutation proposed] src/tic_classifier.py\r\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 024615 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next concrete step for Phase 1. I need to implement a classifier that identifies invariant vs variant content across pulse logs to test the compression-causal duality hypothesis.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"wild-mist","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 4568\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='src/tic_classifier.py' new_len=3142\r\n[mutation proposed] src/tic_classifier.py\r\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 024615 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next concrete step for Phase 1. I need to implement a classifier that identifies invariant vs variant content across pulse logs to test the compression-causal duality hypothesis.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774334803326}}
{"type":"message","id":"7dbb4a53","parentId":"e50cfa10","timestamp":"2026-03-24T06:46:43.330Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_etq9p7lrpq1l_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"﻿# Pulse: 2026-03-24 024413\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\nRejected: src/tic-classifier.ps1 (missing)\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLet me analyze the current state and determine the most impactful next action.\r\n\r\nLooking at the goals:\r\n- Phase 0 and Phase 1 are marked COMPLETE\r\n- There's a pending TIC Experiment (Temporal Invariance Compression) that needs to be implemented\r\n- The key insight is that compression and causal discovery are the same problem\r\n\r\nThe most concrete next action from the pending list is:\r\n\"Implement TIC classifier on `logs/pulse_*.md` files\"\r\n\r\nI should create a TIC experiment implementation. Let me look at what files exist:\r\n- pulse logs in `logs/pulse_*.md`\r\n- The research docs already created\r\n\r\nI need to implement the TIC classifier. This would be a new script that:\r\n1. Reads the pulse logs\r\n2. Classifies content as invariant (stable, persistent) vs variant (changing)\r\n3. Tests prediction accuracy\r\n\r\nLet me create a concrete implementation for this. I'll write a PowerShell script that performs the TIC experiment.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the critical next step to validate the compression-causal duality hypothesis. The pulse logs exist but no classifier has been implemented yet to test invariant/variant classification and next-pulse prediction.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate `tic/classifier.ps1` - a PowerShell script that implements the Temporal Invariance Compression classifier to analyze pulse logs, classify invariant vs variant content, and measure prediction accuracy against the success criteria (>70% classification, >60% prediction).\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # Temporal Invariance Compression (TIC) Classifier\r\n# Implements Phase 1 advancement: compression = causal discovery\r\n# Success Criteria: >70% invariant/variant classification, >60% next-pulse prediction\r\n\r\nparam(\r\n    [int]$Lookback = 5,           # Number of past pulses to analyze\r\n    [int]$MinOccurrence = 3,       # Minimum occurrences to qualify as invariant\r\n    [float]$Threshold = 0.7        # Î» parameter: decay/gap sensitivity\r\n)\r\n\r\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Stop\"\r\n$ScriptDir = Split-Path -Parent $MyInvocation.MyCommand.Path\r\n$RootDir = Split-Path -Parent $ScriptDir\r\n$LogsDir = Join-Path $RootDir \"logs\"\r\n\r\n# --- Helper Functions ---\r\n\r\nfunction Get-PulseLogs {\r\n    param([int]$Count)\r\n    Get-ChildItem -Path $LogsDir -Filter \"pulse_*.md\" |\r\n        Sort-Object LastWriteTime -Descending |\r\n        Select-Object -First $Count\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Extract-NounPhrases {\r\n    param([string]$Text)\r\n    # Simple extraction: capitalized phrases, code identifiers, key terms\r\n    $patterns = @(\r\n        '\\b[A-Z][a-z]+(?:\\s+[A-Z][a-z]+)*\\b',  # Capitalized phrases\r\n        '`[^`]+`',                               # Inline code\r\n        '\\b\\w+_\\w+\\b',                           # snake_case\r\n        '\\b\\w+\\.\\w+\\b',                          # dotted.names\r\n        '\\b(?:Phase|Goal|Insight|Action|Task)\\b' # Domain keywords\r\n    )\r\n    $extracted = @()\r\n    foreach ($p in $patterns) {\r\n        $extracted += [regex]::Matches($Text, $p) | ForEach-Object { $_.Value }\r\n    }\r\n    return ($extracted | Sort-Object -Unique)\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Measure-Invariance {\r\n    param([string[]]$Phrases, [array]$PastPulses)\r\n    \r\n    $invariant = @()\r\n    $variant = @()\r\n    \r\n    foreach ($phrase in $Phrases) {\r\n        $occurrences = 0\r\n        foreach ($pulse in $PastPulses) {\r\n            if ((Get-Content $pulse.FullName -Raw) -match [regex]::Escape($phrase)) {\r\n                $occurrences++\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        $rate = $occurrences / $PastPulses.Count\r\n        \r\n        if ($rate -ge $Threshold) {\r\n            $invariant += @{ Phrase = $phrase; Rate = $rate }\r\n        } else {\r\n            $variant += @{ Phrase = $phrase; Rate = $rate }\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    return @{\r\n        Invariant = $invariant\r\n        Variant = $variant\r\n        ClassificationRate = if ($Phrases.Count -gt 0) { $invariant.Count / $Phrases.Count } else { 0 }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Predict-NextPulse {\r\n    param([array]$Invariants, [string[]]$CurrentPhrases)\r\n    \r\n    # Predict: invariants from past should persist into next pulse\r\n    $predicted = $Invariants | Where-Object { $_.Rate -ge 0.8 }\r\n    $actual = $CurrentPhrases | Where-Object { $_ -in $Invariants.Phrase }\r\n    \r\n    $precision = if ($predicted.Count -gt 0) { $actual.Count / $predicted.Count } else { 0 }\r\n    return @{ Precision = $precision; Predicted = $predicted; Actual = $actual }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# --- Main Experiment ---\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"=== TIC Experiment: Temporal Invariance Compression ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\r\nWrite-Host \"Parameters: Lookback=$Lookback, MinOccurrence=$MinOccurrence, Threshold=$Threshold\"\r\nWrite-Host \"\"\r\n\r\n$pulseLogs = Get-PulseLogs -Count ($Lookback + 1)\r\nif ($pulseLogs.Count -lt 2) {\r\n    Write-Host \"ERROR: Insufficient pulse logs. Need at least 2.\" -ForegroundColor Red\r\n    exit 1\r\n}\r\n\r\n$currentPulse = $pulseLogs[0]\r\n$pastPulses = $pulseLogs[1..($pulseLogs.Count - 1)]\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"Current pulse: $($\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 02:44:43\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774334803328}}
